WEBVTT

00:00:40.840 --> 00:00:42.519
Fang Chi.

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:47.979
Fang Chi.

00:00:49.520 --> 00:00:51.580
Fang Chi.

00:00:52.720 --> 00:00:54.980
Are you afraid?

00:00:59.640 --> 00:01:01.680
Fang Chi.

00:01:01.680 --> 00:01:03.560
Zhang Zhun.

00:01:03.560 --> 00:01:05.720
You're drunk.

00:01:05.720 --> 00:01:08.580
We're not filming right now.

00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:13.100
Are you afraid?

00:01:14.840 --> 00:01:16.080
No.

00:01:16.080 --> 00:01:17.320
I can't.

00:01:17.320 --> 00:01:19.472
That means you're willing.

00:01:26.040 --> 00:01:27.920
Zhang Zhun, wake the hell up.

00:01:27.920 --> 00:01:30.404
I'm Zhen Xin, not Fang Chi.

00:01:40.360 --> 00:01:41.996
Kiss me.

00:01:44.440 --> 00:01:46.540
Say the next line.

00:01:48.960 --> 00:01:51.020
Say your line.

00:01:52.400 --> 00:01:54.620
Say that you need me.

00:01:55.440 --> 00:01:57.074
I...

00:01:58.200 --> 00:02:00.130
Need you.

00:02:29.938 --> 00:02:37.036
[Xie Dan Yi]

00:03:59.736 --> 00:04:03.344
[Episode 3]

00:04:15.320 --> 00:04:18.440
- Hello? <i>- Hello, Mr. Zhang? Still asleep?</i>

00:04:18.440 --> 00:04:20.880
<i>You're due for makeup in half an hour. Get up now.</i>

00:04:20.880 --> 00:04:22.000
<i>Okay, I'll be right there.</i>

00:04:22.000 --> 00:04:25.020
<i>- Mr. Zhang, hurry up.</i> - Okay.

00:05:26.000 --> 00:05:28.302
<i>Say the next line.</i>

00:05:29.920 --> 00:05:31.922
<i>Say your line.</i>

00:05:34.120 --> 00:05:36.463
<i>Say that you need me.</i>

00:06:42.800 --> 00:06:44.942
What have I done?

00:06:54.120 --> 00:06:56.760
I must be losing it from memorizing lines.

00:06:56.760 --> 00:06:58.913
What a ridiculous dream.

00:07:00.080 --> 00:07:01.920
Wake up.

00:07:17.857 --> 00:07:19.692
[Xie Dan Yi]

00:07:22.600 --> 00:07:24.600
Hey, Dan Yi.

00:07:24.600 --> 00:07:25.680
I'm sorry.

00:07:25.680 --> 00:07:27.080
I just saw your calls.

00:07:27.080 --> 00:07:28.939
My phone was on silent last night.

00:07:30.040 --> 00:07:31.526
<i>I'm leaving.</i>

00:07:33.960 --> 00:07:34.997
What?

00:07:34.997 --> 00:07:36.120
[Xie Dan Yi]

00:07:36.120 --> 00:07:39.160
<i>I was in Coconut City last night and called you all night.</i>

00:07:39.160 --> 00:07:40.864
<i>But you didn't pick up.</i>

00:07:41.680 --> 00:07:43.240
<i>I bought a ticket for an early flight.</i>

00:07:43.240 --> 00:07:44.760
<i>I'm at the airport now.</i>

00:07:44.760 --> 00:07:45.880
I'm sorry, Dan Yi.

00:07:45.880 --> 00:07:47.360
The crew went out for drinks last night.

00:07:47.360 --> 00:07:48.920
I got too drunk.

00:07:48.920 --> 00:07:52.413
Why didn't you text me before you came?

00:07:52.413 --> 00:07:54.120
<i>Zhang Zhun.</i>

00:07:54.120 --> 00:07:56.335
<i>I don't know how to describe it.</i>

00:07:57.240 --> 00:07:59.400
<i>I just feel like...</i>

00:07:59.400 --> 00:08:01.080
<i>I feel like I'm losing you.</i>

00:08:01.080 --> 00:08:02.905
What are you talking about?

00:08:03.720 --> 00:08:05.640
<i>Tell me.</i>

00:08:05.640 --> 00:08:07.987
<i>Have you met someone else?</i>

00:08:11.480 --> 00:08:15.360
Who would I meet on a film set?

00:08:15.360 --> 00:08:16.960
<i>Right.</i>

00:08:16.960 --> 00:08:19.400
<i>You're on set.</i>

00:08:19.400 --> 00:08:21.600
<i>But I just feel like...</i>

00:08:21.600 --> 00:08:23.960
<i>you're drifting further and further away.</i>

00:08:23.960 --> 00:08:25.200
<i>Tell me.</i>

00:08:25.200 --> 00:08:26.927
<i>Why is that?</i>

00:08:30.293 --> 00:08:31.953
Don't overthink it.

00:08:31.953 --> 00:08:33.520
I'm just...

00:08:33.520 --> 00:08:35.039
Too immersed in my role.

00:08:37.680 --> 00:08:39.040
Who is it?

00:08:39.040 --> 00:08:41.880
Mr. Zhang, can you come for makeup now?

00:08:41.880 --> 00:08:43.680
Coming!

00:08:43.680 --> 00:08:46.080
Dan Yi, I have to get my makeup done.

00:08:46.080 --> 00:08:48.040
We start filming today.

00:08:48.040 --> 00:08:49.120
Stay safe.

00:08:49.120 --> 00:08:51.011
Text me when you arrive.

00:09:21.160 --> 00:09:24.080
Mr. Zhang, you didn't take off the clip.

00:09:24.080 --> 00:09:26.466
- Thanks. - You're welcome.

00:09:33.400 --> 00:09:34.520
Mr. Zhen.

00:09:34.520 --> 00:09:36.951
Did you take me back to the hotel last night?

00:09:39.640 --> 00:09:40.760
Thank you.

00:09:40.760 --> 00:09:42.160
I drank too much last night.

00:09:42.160 --> 00:09:44.504
I don't even remember you being at the karaoke.

00:09:48.898 --> 00:09:50.496
Well...

00:09:51.480 --> 00:09:54.680
I didn't cause any trouble for you, did I?

00:09:54.680 --> 00:09:56.997
You don't remember anything from last night?

00:09:59.600 --> 00:10:02.540
I didn't do anything to offend you, did I?

00:10:09.400 --> 00:10:12.042
If you can't hold your liquor, drink less in the future.

00:10:13.480 --> 00:10:15.000
Mr. Zhang.

00:10:15.000 --> 00:10:16.120
We need to head to the set.

00:10:16.120 --> 00:10:17.120
The director is asking for us.

00:10:17.120 --> 00:10:19.440
Oh, okay. Let's go.

00:10:37.136 --> 00:10:40.812
[Zuo Lin Lin]

00:10:48.920 --> 00:10:50.280
Lin Lin, I'll say it one more time.

00:10:50.280 --> 00:10:51.795
Asking me, your ex, to provide therapy

00:10:51.795 --> 00:10:54.000
For your current boyfriend is inappropriate.

00:10:54.000 --> 00:10:55.280
<i>Charles.</i>

00:10:55.280 --> 00:10:57.000
<i>I want to make things work with him.</i>

00:10:57.000 --> 00:10:59.640
<i>For the sake of what we once had, please help me.</i>

00:10:59.640 --> 00:11:01.880
There are many causes for insomnia.

00:11:01.880 --> 00:11:03.320
It's not necessarily a psychological issue.

00:11:03.320 --> 00:11:05.320
You should take him to a hospital first.

00:11:05.320 --> 00:11:06.680
<i>Charles.</i>

00:11:06.680 --> 00:11:09.120
<i>The hospital said his physical examinations were all normal.</i>

00:11:09.120 --> 00:11:10.800
<i>And it's not just insomnia.</i>

00:11:10.800 --> 00:11:12.733
<i>He's afraid of the dark and enclosed spaces.</i>

00:11:12.733 --> 00:11:14.000
<i>He doesn't even dare to drive.</i>

00:11:14.000 --> 00:11:16.120
<i>He won't even go to underground parking.</i>

00:11:16.120 --> 00:11:17.640
<i>He also has frequent nightmares.</i>

00:11:17.640 --> 00:11:19.000
<i>I'm really at my wit's end.</i>

00:11:19.000 --> 00:11:20.916
<i>Otherwise, I wouldn't have come to you.</i>

00:11:21.960 --> 00:11:23.360
What other symptoms does he have?

00:11:23.360 --> 00:11:25.200
<i>He's often absent-minded.</i>

00:11:25.200 --> 00:11:26.680
<i>He drinks every night.</i>

00:11:26.680 --> 00:11:29.160
<i>And I found sleeping pills in the liquor cabinet.</i>

00:11:29.160 --> 00:11:31.840
<i>Half the bottle is already gone.</i>

00:11:31.840 --> 00:11:33.440
Did he use to drink?

00:11:33.440 --> 00:11:34.960
<i>Very rarely.</i>

00:11:34.960 --> 00:11:37.440
<i>A bottle of red wine every two months.</i>

00:11:37.440 --> 00:11:41.080
<i>But lately, the liquor cabinet is filled with new bottles.</i>

00:11:41.080 --> 00:11:43.080
How is your relationship?

00:11:43.080 --> 00:11:44.080
<i>Us?</i>

00:11:44.080 --> 00:11:45.488
In every aspect.

00:11:46.440 --> 00:11:48.720
<i>We're fine.</i>

00:11:48.720 --> 00:11:51.160
<i>Just like any normal couple.</i>

00:11:51.160 --> 00:11:53.400
<i>It's just that when I initiate intimacy,</i>

00:11:53.400 --> 00:11:55.080
<i>he doesn't respond.</i>

00:11:55.080 --> 00:11:56.240
<i>Charles.</i>

00:11:56.240 --> 00:11:58.473
<i>Can you see him today?</i>

00:12:01.480 --> 00:12:03.039
<i>Charles.</i>

00:12:05.720 --> 00:12:08.080
Tell him to come after four.

00:12:08.080 --> 00:12:09.760
<i>That's great. Thank you.</i>

00:12:09.760 --> 00:12:11.600
<i>I'll tell him right away.</i>

00:12:11.600 --> 00:12:12.760
<i>Thank you so much.</i>

00:12:12.760 --> 00:12:14.433
What's his name?

00:12:14.433 --> 00:12:15.981
<i>Gao Zhun.</i>

00:12:31.240 --> 00:12:34.200
<i>Dr. Fang, Mr. Gao is here.</i>

00:12:34.200 --> 00:12:36.040
Isn't he early?

00:12:36.040 --> 00:12:37.760
<i>It's okay, Ms. Feng.</i>

00:12:37.760 --> 00:12:38.920
<i>My appointment is at four.</i>

00:12:38.920 --> 00:12:40.462
<i>I can wait a while.</i>

00:12:45.760 --> 00:12:47.030
Please, come in.

00:13:04.760 --> 00:13:06.040
Nice to meet you, Dr. Fang.

00:13:06.040 --> 00:13:07.931
Hello, Mr. Gao.

00:13:13.920 --> 00:13:15.970
Please have a seat, Mr. Gao.

00:13:46.560 --> 00:13:48.997
What do you do for a living, Mr. Gao?

00:13:50.760 --> 00:13:52.435
Art investment.

00:13:53.640 --> 00:13:55.426
You studied art?

00:13:56.880 --> 00:13:58.520
Art management.

00:13:58.520 --> 00:14:00.512
I've done woodblock prints.

00:14:07.560 --> 00:14:09.598
Is something wrong, Mr. Gao?

00:14:10.840 --> 00:14:11.914
No.

00:14:12.880 --> 00:14:14.248
It's nothing.

00:14:16.136 --> 00:14:19.862
[Claustrophobia]

00:14:20.640 --> 00:14:22.920
You and Lin Lin are a couple?

00:14:24.200 --> 00:14:26.071
She's my fiancée.

00:14:28.840 --> 00:14:30.320
I heard from her

00:14:30.320 --> 00:14:32.920
That you've been having insomnia lately.

00:14:32.920 --> 00:14:34.932
Have you tried sleeping pills?

00:14:36.800 --> 00:14:38.660
I have.

00:14:39.320 --> 00:14:41.120
They don't work.

00:14:41.120 --> 00:14:43.060
I have nightmares.

00:14:57.600 --> 00:14:59.265
What do you dream about?

00:15:00.260 --> 00:15:01.933
I dream about...

00:15:03.320 --> 00:15:05.572
Being alone in a parking lot.

00:15:15.480 --> 00:15:17.800
It's okay.

00:15:17.800 --> 00:15:20.998
In here, you're safe.

00:15:22.560 --> 00:15:24.033
I...

00:15:25.560 --> 00:15:26.983
I'm sorry.

00:15:27.920 --> 00:15:29.436
You're scared.

00:15:32.240 --> 00:15:34.400
No.

00:15:34.400 --> 00:15:36.066
It's just...

00:15:37.440 --> 00:15:39.506
You're too close to me.

00:15:47.240 --> 00:15:49.034
I can help you.

00:15:50.200 --> 00:15:52.057
But first,

00:15:53.160 --> 00:15:54.979
You have to trust me.

00:15:56.360 --> 00:15:58.060
Do you understand?

00:16:03.440 --> 00:16:04.942
Good.

00:16:05.960 --> 00:16:07.520
Come.

00:16:07.520 --> 00:16:09.200
Repeat after me.

00:16:09.200 --> 00:16:11.469
"Okay, Dr. Fang."

00:16:17.280 --> 00:16:19.454
Okay, Dr. Fang.

00:16:25.040 --> 00:16:28.399
Mr. Gao, that's all for today.

00:16:29.400 --> 00:16:30.552
Okay.

00:16:41.720 --> 00:16:44.160
Dr. Fang, I'll see you next week.

00:16:44.160 --> 00:16:45.518
Wait.

00:16:55.680 --> 00:16:57.560
Take this and apply it to your eyes.

00:16:57.560 --> 00:16:59.040
They're all swollen.

00:17:08.640 --> 00:17:10.009
See you next week.

00:17:22.760 --> 00:17:26.040
<i>Charles, what exactly is his illness?</i>

00:17:26.040 --> 00:17:27.935
I'm not sure yet.

00:17:29.680 --> 00:17:34.478
But I suspect it's not just a mental illness.

00:17:37.133 --> 00:17:39.680
[Zuo Lin Lin]

00:17:39.680 --> 00:17:42.360
Has he had any traumatic experiences?

00:17:42.360 --> 00:17:47.800
For example, being robbed or kidnapped?

00:17:47.800 --> 00:17:49.960
<i>I don't know.</i>

00:17:49.960 --> 00:17:53.439
<i>I don't understand why he won't tell me what's really wrong with him.</i>

00:17:54.760 --> 00:17:58.233
<i>Charles, what should I do?</i>

00:17:58.233 --> 00:18:00.640
He needs someone.

00:18:00.640 --> 00:18:03.920
An absolutely powerful guide.

00:18:03.920 --> 00:18:06.985
Someone to lead him out of the prison of his mind.

00:18:25.720 --> 00:18:26.920
Get in.

00:18:26.920 --> 00:18:28.381
I'll give you a ride.

00:18:35.920 --> 00:18:37.000
No, thank you.

00:18:37.000 --> 00:18:40.440
I... I can walk back.

00:18:40.440 --> 00:18:41.800
It's not far.

00:18:41.800 --> 00:18:43.938
<i>He's afraid of the dark and enclosed spaces.</i>

00:18:43.938 --> 00:18:45.280
<i>He doesn't even dare to drive.</i>

00:18:45.280 --> 00:18:47.960
<i>He won't even go to underground parking.</i>

00:18:47.960 --> 00:18:49.520
All right then.

00:18:49.520 --> 00:18:50.720
Take care.

00:18:50.720 --> 00:18:52.298
See you next week.

00:18:53.880 --> 00:18:55.040
Okay.

00:18:55.040 --> 00:18:56.554
See you next week.

00:19:01.360 --> 00:19:07.040
However, if you ever need help, you can call me, too.

00:19:07.040 --> 00:19:09.660
Even if it's three in the morning.

00:20:10.519 --> 00:20:13.231
So, during your childhood,

00:20:13.231 --> 00:20:15.481
Only your mother was around.

00:20:16.760 --> 00:20:19.073
Did she have any other partners?

00:20:20.320 --> 00:20:21.980
She did.

00:20:23.480 --> 00:20:26.520
A tall, well-built man.

00:20:26.520 --> 00:20:28.432
He was a bit like you.

00:20:29.480 --> 00:20:31.720
He was a good man.

00:20:31.720 --> 00:20:33.355
But...

00:20:34.680 --> 00:20:36.521
He left later on.

00:20:38.880 --> 00:20:41.231
My mother was devastated.

00:20:46.880 --> 00:20:49.385
Did your mother put a lot of pressure on you?

00:20:50.280 --> 00:20:52.560
She wanted me to be superior to others.

00:20:52.560 --> 00:20:55.019
I know she did it for my own good.

00:20:56.280 --> 00:20:57.943
So...

00:20:58.920 --> 00:21:01.521
I always did exactly as she wanted.

00:21:02.600 --> 00:21:04.640
Is this important?

00:21:04.640 --> 00:21:06.880
Very important.

00:21:06.880 --> 00:21:09.029
I used to cry a lot as a child.

00:21:11.280 --> 00:21:13.544
My mom would make me hold it in.

00:21:25.379 --> 00:21:30.433
She said, "A real man shouldn't act like a woman."

00:21:36.840 --> 00:21:39.080
Very good.

00:21:39.080 --> 00:21:41.560
You're being very cooperative.

00:21:41.560 --> 00:21:43.387
Now...

00:21:45.280 --> 00:21:47.462
Tell me about your nightmares.

00:21:53.080 --> 00:21:56.880
With me, you are safe.

00:21:56.880 --> 00:21:59.049
This is a secret between us.

00:22:03.200 --> 00:22:06.720
Every word you say to me in this clinic,

00:22:06.720 --> 00:22:09.047
I will keep confidential.

00:22:10.040 --> 00:22:14.081
As long as... you don't break the law.

00:22:18.040 --> 00:22:20.240
What if I fantasize about a crime,

00:22:20.240 --> 00:22:22.104
But don't actually commit it?

00:22:23.440 --> 00:22:25.071
Or...

00:22:26.160 --> 00:22:28.482
What if I'm the victim?

00:22:29.640 --> 00:22:34.501
You have to trust me, just as I trust you.

00:22:35.800 --> 00:22:39.981
You'll help me, won't you?

00:22:41.120 --> 00:22:43.140
I will.

00:22:49.400 --> 00:22:51.720
Nightmares belong to the darkness.

00:22:51.720 --> 00:22:54.600
Only by entering that darkness

00:22:54.600 --> 00:22:56.896
Can I interpret your nightmares.

00:22:59.320 --> 00:23:01.200
From this moment on,

00:23:01.200 --> 00:23:03.160
The tie in my hand

00:23:03.160 --> 00:23:05.541
Will be your tether to me. [Victimization, M tendencies]

00:23:10.520 --> 00:23:12.436
Feel it.

00:23:13.560 --> 00:23:16.041
It's as if I'm right by your side.

00:23:18.600 --> 00:23:22.972
If you're ready, close your eyes.

00:23:30.880 --> 00:23:32.520
Very good.

00:23:32.520 --> 00:23:37.524
Now, take me into your nightmare.

00:23:38.520 --> 00:23:40.340
Cut!

00:23:44.995 --> 00:23:46.040
I'll take that.

00:23:46.040 --> 00:23:47.320
Mr. Zhen.

00:23:47.320 --> 00:23:48.880
Was my performance okay just now?

00:23:48.880 --> 00:23:50.320
It was good.

00:23:50.320 --> 00:23:51.960
Very good.

00:23:51.960 --> 00:23:54.120
Next, we'll move to the next scene.

00:23:54.120 --> 00:23:56.680
You two go and change first.

00:23:56.680 --> 00:23:57.720
You go ahead.

00:23:57.720 --> 00:23:59.363
I'm going for a smoke.

00:24:02.840 --> 00:24:05.040
Zhang Zhun, go and change your costume and makeup first.

00:24:05.040 --> 00:24:07.600
Next, we're filming the later scene in the counseling room.

00:24:07.600 --> 00:24:09.600
The intimate scene between Fang Chi and Gao Zhun.

00:24:09.600 --> 00:24:11.440
Okay.

00:24:11.440 --> 00:24:14.160
You're in great form today. Very sharp.

00:24:14.160 --> 00:24:16.148
Keep it up.

00:24:31.600 --> 00:24:33.640
Is he pretending nothing happened,

00:24:33.640 --> 00:24:35.960
Or did he really black out?

00:24:35.960 --> 00:24:37.473
Damn it.

00:24:40.800 --> 00:24:43.338
How can we film if he's like this every time?

00:24:54.440 --> 00:24:55.840
Mr. Zhen.

00:24:55.840 --> 00:24:57.240
What's wrong?

00:24:57.240 --> 00:25:00.080
I felt a bit unwell just now, so I washed my face.

00:25:00.080 --> 00:25:01.200
Touch up my makeup, please.

00:25:01.200 --> 00:25:02.240
You got it.

00:25:02.240 --> 00:25:04.350
Mr. Zhang, you're all set.

00:25:25.360 --> 00:25:27.520
Are you unwell? Do you have a fever?

00:25:27.520 --> 00:25:28.520
I have some medicine.

00:25:28.520 --> 00:25:30.160
I'll bring it to you when we get back.

00:25:30.160 --> 00:25:31.720
No need.

00:25:31.720 --> 00:25:33.773
I'm a grown man. I'm not that fragile.

00:25:33.773 --> 00:25:35.440
Don't ignore it when you're sick.

00:25:35.440 --> 00:25:36.921
I'll...

00:25:46.880 --> 00:25:48.480
All right, get ready.

00:25:48.480 --> 00:25:49.640
Dao, adjust the lights.

00:25:49.640 --> 00:25:50.992
We're about to start filming.

00:25:51.840 --> 00:25:53.405
You'll what?

00:25:55.160 --> 00:25:57.160
I'll worry.

00:25:57.160 --> 00:25:59.100
Action!

00:26:13.360 --> 00:26:14.760
Who's calling?

00:26:14.760 --> 00:26:15.800
Is it Lin Lin?

00:26:15.800 --> 00:26:17.240
[Zuo Lin Lin]

00:26:19.280 --> 00:26:21.035
It doesn't matter.

00:26:32.840 --> 00:26:35.960
Zhang Zhun, lift your head up.

00:26:35.960 --> 00:26:36.960
Director.

00:26:36.960 --> 00:26:39.360
Zhang Zhun is getting the short end of the stick here.

00:26:39.360 --> 00:26:40.640
Short end of the stick?

00:26:40.640 --> 00:26:43.080
Actresses filming bed scenes have it worse.

00:26:43.080 --> 00:26:44.280
True.

00:26:44.280 --> 00:26:47.360
But Mr. Zhen didn't join us for karaoke yesterday.

00:26:47.360 --> 00:26:48.720
I've noticed several times today...

00:26:48.720 --> 00:26:50.560
That they aren't getting along.

00:26:50.560 --> 00:26:52.200
If their relationship is strained...

00:26:52.200 --> 00:26:54.920
- Then... - They're actors.

00:26:54.920 --> 00:26:57.400
No matter how bad things are privately,

00:26:57.400 --> 00:26:58.800
As long as they're in character,

00:26:58.800 --> 00:27:00.120
And they're immersed,

00:27:00.120 --> 00:27:02.240
It'll work.

00:27:02.240 --> 00:27:03.780
Right.

00:27:10.720 --> 00:27:11.840
Cut!

00:27:11.840 --> 00:27:14.000
Great. That's a wrap for this scene.

00:27:14.000 --> 00:27:16.960
- Wrap it up! - Thank you, Director.

00:27:32.120 --> 00:27:34.599
Is something the matter?

00:27:34.599 --> 00:27:36.504
I brought some medicine over.

00:27:38.320 --> 00:27:39.600
No need.

00:27:39.600 --> 00:27:41.539
I'm much better now.

00:28:18.320 --> 00:28:21.881
He wants to play this push-and-pull game.

00:28:22.800 --> 00:28:25.525
He won't be direct and won't mention it.

00:28:27.200 --> 00:28:30.040
Let's see who can hold out longer.

00:28:30.040 --> 00:28:32.280
I am Zhen Xin.

00:28:32.280 --> 00:28:35.100
The Best Actor.

00:28:38.080 --> 00:28:40.560
Zhen Xin, I think this scene was good.

00:28:40.560 --> 00:28:42.200
That's thanks to your vision.

00:28:42.200 --> 00:28:45.440
Just stick to the script and we're good.

00:28:45.440 --> 00:28:46.880
Morning, Director.

00:28:46.880 --> 00:28:48.545
Morning, Mr. Zhen.

00:28:55.000 --> 00:28:57.200
Director, I'm heading to makeup.

00:28:57.200 --> 00:28:58.200
No rush, no rush.

00:28:58.200 --> 00:29:00.480
We're not following the call sheet for today's shoot.

00:29:00.480 --> 00:29:03.080
We'll shoot the scene with Fang Chi and Zuo Lin Lin first.

00:29:03.080 --> 00:29:04.440
Then Gao Zhun's solo scenes.

00:29:04.440 --> 00:29:06.840
The scene between you and Mr. Zhen...

00:29:06.840 --> 00:29:08.640
We'll save that for last.

00:29:08.640 --> 00:29:10.760
Thanks, Director. I'll head back then.

00:29:10.760 --> 00:29:12.057
Keep it up!

00:29:17.920 --> 00:29:19.560
I can't believe this.

00:29:19.560 --> 00:29:20.720
We pulled an all-nighter for this set,

00:29:20.720 --> 00:29:23.360
Only for their scenes to be pushed to last.

00:29:23.360 --> 00:29:24.840
What a load of crap.

00:29:24.840 --> 00:29:27.560
Why the delay? Weren't they acting well together?

00:29:27.560 --> 00:29:29.080
Well?

00:29:29.080 --> 00:29:30.720
Haven't you heard the rumors?

00:29:30.720 --> 00:29:32.880
Zhang Zhun is just clinging to Mr. Zhen.

00:29:32.880 --> 00:29:35.404
I heard the Best Actor is fed up with him.

00:29:36.440 --> 00:29:37.960
No way.

00:29:37.960 --> 00:29:41.200
When I saw them filming, they seemed really into it.

00:29:41.200 --> 00:29:43.360
Mr. Zhen seemed quite comfortable, too.

00:29:43.360 --> 00:29:44.720
Comfortable?

00:29:44.720 --> 00:29:46.400
That's just Mr. Zhen's acting skills.

00:29:46.400 --> 00:29:47.920
If they were actually close,

00:29:47.920 --> 00:29:51.000
Would he ask the director to postpone the intimate scenes?

00:29:51.000 --> 00:29:53.240
He just doesn't want to deal with that guy.

00:29:53.240 --> 00:29:54.880
As for being comfortable...

00:29:54.880 --> 00:29:57.960
You have to give it your all to get famous.

00:29:57.960 --> 00:29:59.680
I feel bad for Mr. Zhen.

00:29:59.680 --> 00:30:03.080
Having to hug and hold someone older than him.

00:30:03.080 --> 00:30:04.600
I heard after every take,

00:30:04.600 --> 00:30:06.400
He has to hide in the bathroom for ages.

00:30:06.400 --> 00:30:08.500
He's probably totally grossed out.

00:30:21.320 --> 00:30:22.680
Mr. Zhen.

00:30:22.680 --> 00:30:24.511
I'd like to talk to you.

00:30:26.760 --> 00:30:28.480
Go ahead.

00:30:28.480 --> 00:30:31.000
Did I do something wrong?

00:30:31.000 --> 00:30:33.320
Did I make you uncomfortable?

00:30:33.320 --> 00:30:34.895
No.

00:30:36.600 --> 00:30:40.040
Then why... do you seem to be avoiding me?

00:30:40.040 --> 00:30:42.080
Shit.

00:30:42.080 --> 00:30:45.120
The prism ball didn't work for the color.

00:30:45.120 --> 00:30:47.840
Mr. Zhen, we'll shoot your first solo scene in a moment.

00:30:47.840 --> 00:30:50.760
Once Mr. Wu Rong arrives, we'll move on to your scene with him.

00:30:50.760 --> 00:30:52.760
Is Wu Rong joining the set today?

00:30:52.760 --> 00:30:54.033
I thought it wasn't until the weekend.

00:30:54.033 --> 00:30:55.520
Ms. Qin had a last-minute event.

00:30:55.520 --> 00:30:56.560
The schedule was adjusted.

00:30:56.560 --> 00:30:59.080
So, Mr. Wu is joining us early.

00:30:59.080 --> 00:31:00.522
I'm going to rehearse.

00:31:06.200 --> 00:31:08.081
Are you two okay?

00:31:23.840 --> 00:31:25.416
Mr. Zhen.

00:31:32.039 --> 00:31:33.400
Damn.

00:31:33.400 --> 00:31:35.063
He's so damn handsome.

00:32:07.240 --> 00:32:09.060
Are you okay?

00:32:10.440 --> 00:32:12.602
Are you crazy? You could've died!

00:32:13.840 --> 00:32:15.240
I'm fine.

00:32:15.240 --> 00:32:17.440
I'm trained for this.

00:32:17.440 --> 00:32:18.760
What happened?

00:32:18.760 --> 00:32:20.760
Zhang Zhun, are you okay?

00:32:20.760 --> 00:32:23.180
Zhou Zheng, call an ambulance!

00:32:23.920 --> 00:32:26.080
Director, it's a prop, not the real thing.

00:32:26.080 --> 00:32:27.160
Mr. Zhang, are you okay?

00:32:27.160 --> 00:32:28.480
Where are you hurt? Do we need an ambulance?

00:32:28.480 --> 00:32:29.982
No need.

00:32:31.840 --> 00:32:33.480
No, it hit your back.

00:32:33.480 --> 00:32:34.640
You must go to the hospital.

00:32:34.640 --> 00:32:37.000
It's fine. This happens to stuntmen often.

00:32:37.000 --> 00:32:39.280
Zhang Zhun, how are you feeling right now?

00:32:39.280 --> 00:32:40.720
Will it affect tomorrow's shoot?

00:32:40.720 --> 00:32:41.720
Chen!

00:32:41.720 --> 00:32:44.360
He just got crushed!

00:32:44.360 --> 00:32:45.477
Zhun.

00:32:46.400 --> 00:32:48.560
How are you, Zhun? Are you hurt?

00:32:48.560 --> 00:32:50.120
I'm fine.

00:32:50.120 --> 00:32:52.000
I just got hit by a prop steel pipe.

00:32:52.000 --> 00:32:55.040
I'm really okay. I'm fine, Director.

00:32:55.040 --> 00:32:56.440
What's the deal, Director Chen?

00:32:56.440 --> 00:32:57.920
Are you bullying my junior?

00:32:57.920 --> 00:32:59.760
Mr. Wu, please don't say that.

00:32:59.760 --> 00:33:02.970
Zhang Zhun rushed over to save Mr. Zhen.

00:33:04.480 --> 00:33:06.000
Mr. Zhen.

00:33:06.000 --> 00:33:07.840
My junior is bullied by you in the show,

00:33:07.840 --> 00:33:09.400
Yet he protects you like this in real life.

00:33:09.400 --> 00:33:11.720
If he's actually injured,

00:33:11.720 --> 00:33:13.840
I'll have to count on you to take care of him.

00:33:13.840 --> 00:33:16.680
Stop it, Wu Rong. I just need some ointment.

00:33:16.680 --> 00:33:19.120
Everyone needs to film. Don't delay the schedule.

00:33:19.120 --> 00:33:20.200
Right, right.

00:33:20.200 --> 00:33:21.440
- You guys go ahead and film. - Zhun.

00:33:21.440 --> 00:33:22.920
There's medicine in my trailer. Go there now.

00:33:22.920 --> 00:33:24.433
- Go and get that treated. - Okay.

00:33:24.433 --> 00:33:26.640
The trailer is over there.

00:33:26.640 --> 00:33:28.873
- Are you okay? - I'm fine.

00:33:47.440 --> 00:33:49.400
Don't move.

00:33:49.400 --> 00:33:51.560
Why are you here?

00:33:51.560 --> 00:33:53.520
Aren't you supposed to be filming your scene?

00:33:53.520 --> 00:33:54.920
They don't need me yet.

00:33:54.920 --> 00:33:56.477
I came to check on you.

00:34:01.960 --> 00:34:04.440
Just now...

00:34:04.440 --> 00:34:06.760
Thank you for taking the hit for me.

00:34:06.760 --> 00:34:09.000
It's nothing. It's what I should do.

00:34:09.000 --> 00:34:11.760
I couldn't just watch you get hurt.

00:34:11.760 --> 00:34:14.017
I admit...

00:34:14.017 --> 00:34:15.988
I have been avoiding you a little.

00:34:17.160 --> 00:34:18.760
Why?

00:34:18.760 --> 00:34:20.400
Just consider it the sin of holding jade.

00:34:20.400 --> 00:34:22.440
Wh-What?

00:34:22.440 --> 00:34:25.740
Nothing. If you don't remember, forget it.

00:34:26.640 --> 00:34:28.080
I must have been really drunk.

00:34:28.080 --> 00:34:29.840
How did I offend you?

00:34:29.840 --> 00:34:31.440
I'll drink less next time.

00:34:31.440 --> 00:34:32.920
I won't cause you any more trouble.

00:34:32.920 --> 00:34:34.990
Don't move.

00:34:37.440 --> 00:34:39.400
When you were a stunt double,

00:34:39.400 --> 00:34:42.220
Getting injured was a daily occurrence, right?

00:34:43.800 --> 00:34:46.040
I'm used to it.

00:34:46.040 --> 00:34:47.910
You shouldn't be used to it.

00:34:48.960 --> 00:34:50.393
Besides...

00:34:51.560 --> 00:34:53.919
I don't want to see you get hurt.

00:34:59.400 --> 00:35:01.469
Don't you think...

00:35:02.800 --> 00:35:07.839
That line sounds like something Fang Chi would say to Gao Zhun?

00:35:14.040 --> 00:35:16.520
Then, who is talking to you now?

00:35:16.520 --> 00:35:18.640
Is it Fang Chi...

00:35:18.640 --> 00:35:20.388
Or Zhen Xin?

00:35:22.960 --> 00:35:26.080
Mr. Zhen, you're up in the next scene.

00:35:26.080 --> 00:35:27.379
Coming!

00:35:28.280 --> 00:35:29.546
There, all done.

00:35:40.680 --> 00:35:43.240
Director, Zhun is my junior.

00:35:43.240 --> 00:35:46.560
Please look out for him for me.

00:35:46.560 --> 00:35:49.480
Of course. We're all family here.

00:35:49.480 --> 00:35:51.300
Have a drink.

00:35:53.320 --> 00:35:55.200
Come on, Zhun.

00:35:55.200 --> 00:35:56.720
Let's play for high stakes this time.

00:35:56.720 --> 00:35:58.880
We'll compare dice. The one with the lower roll...

00:35:58.880 --> 00:36:00.200
Must answer a question from the winner.

00:36:00.200 --> 00:36:02.600
You must tell the truth.

00:36:02.600 --> 00:36:03.976
All right.

00:36:09.640 --> 00:36:11.560
Here we go.

00:36:11.560 --> 00:36:13.000
Of everyone here...

00:36:13.000 --> 00:36:15.160
Am I the senior who loves you the most?

00:36:15.160 --> 00:36:16.945
The one who takes the best care of you?

00:36:19.200 --> 00:36:20.320
The dice will be our witness.

00:36:20.320 --> 00:36:21.600
You must tell the truth.

00:36:21.600 --> 00:36:22.720
Tell the truth, now.

00:36:22.720 --> 00:36:24.056
Yes.

00:36:45.000 --> 00:36:46.800
That sounds terrible.

00:36:46.800 --> 00:36:48.800
Everyone's getting pretty tipsy.

00:36:48.800 --> 00:36:50.220
Is this game too intimate for you?

00:36:50.220 --> 00:36:51.720
Getting uncomfortable?

00:36:51.720 --> 00:36:54.027
- Drink, drink, drink! - Keep singing, keep singing!

00:37:01.200 --> 00:37:02.280
You should sing, too.

00:37:02.280 --> 00:37:04.000
Come on, sing!

00:37:04.000 --> 00:37:05.480
Don't be such a killjoy.

00:37:05.480 --> 00:37:08.080
At least sing a couple of lines.

00:37:08.080 --> 00:37:09.193
He's had too much to drink.

00:37:09.193 --> 00:37:11.560
Fine, fine. I'll let you off the hook.

00:37:11.560 --> 00:37:12.600
Everyone, up!

00:37:12.600 --> 00:37:14.520
Director Ma's team is upstairs.

00:37:14.520 --> 00:37:16.600
Let's go say hi and have a few drinks.

00:37:16.600 --> 00:37:18.480
Have a few drinks?

00:37:18.480 --> 00:37:20.560
You stay here. We'll be right back.

00:37:20.560 --> 00:37:21.720
Just lie down here for a bit.

00:37:21.720 --> 00:37:23.800
Zhun, don't drink anymore.

00:37:23.800 --> 00:37:26.020
- Okay. - Let's go.

00:37:35.280 --> 00:37:37.693
I really can't take it any more.

00:37:37.693 --> 00:37:40.800
Yun Ting, hurry up and get here.

00:37:40.800 --> 00:37:43.620
If you don't come soon, I might fall for someone else.

00:37:45.600 --> 00:37:47.007
Okay.

00:37:47.007 --> 00:37:48.800
I'll wait for you.

00:37:48.800 --> 00:37:50.322
Bye-bye.

00:38:06.360 --> 00:38:08.200
I told you.

00:38:08.200 --> 00:38:10.560
If you can't hold your liquor, don't drink so much.

00:38:10.560 --> 00:38:12.840
But you just won't listen.

00:38:12.840 --> 00:38:15.080
Kiss me.

00:38:15.080 --> 00:38:18.004
Please, kiss me.

00:38:43.560 --> 00:38:45.069
Zhen Xin...

00:42:27.240 --> 00:42:29.468
How can you be so seductive?

00:42:31.640 --> 00:42:36.034
Because... I need you.

